N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 13 ยง 52.14 - Hearing officer's report; exceptions to report

State Regulations

Upon the conclusion of a hearing the hearing officer shall, by written memorandum
to the Attorney General, set forth his findings and recommendations for action by the Attorney General thereon. Notes
